column1: Utah (PST) SNOTEL Site Timpanogos Divide - NRCS National Water and Climate Center - Provisional Data - subject to revision as of Mon Nov 25 14:58:54 GMT-08:00 2019. Notes on dates - Daily sensors (e.g. TAVG.D-1) report a summary value for the previous day.  Hourly sensors (e.g. TAVG.H-1) report a summary value for the previous hour.  Instantaneous sensors (e.g. TOBS.I-1) report a single observation on the hour.
